extends layout
block main
  .page-header
    h1
      span.icon.glyphicon.glyphicon-list-alt
      | Spreadsheet

  p.lead.
    You can set up your Google Sheet backend here.

  form.form
    .form-group
      span.icon.glyphicon.glyphicon-refresh.spin.pull-right
      label(for="spreadsheet-select")
        | Orders & Inventory spreadsheet
      select#spreadsheet-select.form-control(name="spreadsheet" data-template="#spreadsheet script")
      .help-block.initial.
        Your order and inventory will be kept in this sheet, and the app will
        read and write from/to there. You will have to grant permission!
    .form-group.text-center
      button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary(disabled type="submit" name="choose-spreadsheet") Use this spreadsheet

  script(type="text/html")
    option Select a spreadsheet
    | {{#spreadsheets}}
    option(value="{{id}}") {{{name}}}
    | {{/spreadsheets}}


